#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Follow Mouse Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mode avec suivi de "
"la souris</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode the area around the mouse cursor is shown in a normal window."
msgstr ""
"Dans ce mode, la zone autour du pointeur de souris est affichée dans une "
"fenêtre normale."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Selection Window Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mode de sélection de "
"fenêtre</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode a selection window is opened. The selected area is shown in a "
"normal window."
msgstr ""
"Dans ce mode, une fenêtre de sélection est ouverte. La zone sélectionnée est "
"affichée dans une fenêtre normale."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F4</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Whole Screen Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F4</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mode Plein écran</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this mode the whole screen is magnified in the zoom window."
msgstr ""
"Dans ce mode, l'écran tout entier est agrandi dans la zone de grossissement."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hide Mouse Cursor</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cacher le pointeur "
"de la souris</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415 index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the mouse cursor in the magnified image."
msgstr "Montre ou cache le pointeur de la souris dans l'image grossie."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stays On Top</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Maintenir au dessus</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427 index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kmagnifier; window stays on top of other windows."
msgstr "La fenêtre de &kmagnifier; reste au dessus des autres fenêtres."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kmagnifier; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"En plus, &kmagnifier; possède des éléments communs de menus KDE "
"<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> et <guimenu>Aide</guimenu>. Pour plus "
"d'informations, veuillez consulter les sections <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/ui.html#menus-settings\">Menu de configuration</ulink> et "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-help\">Menu d'aide</ulink> des "
"fondamentaux de &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Référence des commandes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmagnifier; automatically uses all your default shortcuts for saving file, "
"opening new window, printing, starting/stopping refresh (reload button in "
"&konqueror;), zoom-in, zoom-out &etc;"
msgstr ""
"&kmagnifier; utilise automatiquement tous les raccourcis par défaut pour "
"enregistrer un fichier, ouvrir une nouvelle fenêtre, imprimer, "
"démarrer / arrêter le rafraîchissement (bouton « Recharger » dans "
"&konqueror;), zoomer en avant ou en arrière, &etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Raccourcis clavier par défaut"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will save the contents of the zoom window to a file."
msgstr "Enregistrer le contenu de la fenêtre zoomée dans un fichier."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F2</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F2</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to \"Follow Mouse Mode\"."
msgstr "Basculer en « Mode de suivi de la souris »."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F3</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F3</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to \"Selection Window Mode\"."
msgstr "Basculer en mode « grossir une zone »."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F4</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F4</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to \"Whole Screen Mode\"."
msgstr "Basculer en « Grossir l'écran entier »."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F5</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F5</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will start the refresh of the zoom window if it is stopped, or stops "
"the refresh of the zoom window if the refresh is currently on."
msgstr ""
"Démarrer le rafraîchissement de la fenêtre zoomée s'il a été arrête, ou "
"arrêter le rafraîchissement de la fenêtre zoomée s'il était activé."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F6</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F6</keycap>"

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F7</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F7</keycap>"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will open a new &kmagnifier; window."
msgstr "Ceci ouvre une nouvelle fenêtre de &kmagnifier;."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will open the print dialog for printing the contents of the zoom window."
msgstr ""
"Ouvre la boite de dialogue d'impression pour imprimer le contenu de la "
"fenêtre zoomée."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will copy the zoom window contents to the clipboard."
msgstr "Copie le contenu de la fenêtre zoomée dans le presse-papiers."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show/Hide the menubar."
msgstr "Affiche / cache la barre de menu."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom out"
msgstr "Zoom arrière"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom in"
msgstr "Zoom avant"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quits the application."
msgstr "Quitte l'application."

